fields.instructions:
Welcome to our experiment. You will be working together to solve problems and complete tasks.

Your first task is to orient yourself with the interaction window. You will be taken to the next page when the timer at the top right of the page reaches zero. At that page, enter your name about the "Chat" window, and type your name in the "Answer" section of he large text area. Also send a message to other people participating in the experiment
fields.interaction_instructions: Identify yourself by entering a name above the chat window, and send a chat message. Type your name in the main text area

fields.instructions: You will have 2 minutes to memorize as much about the picture that I have handed out as possible. Since this task tests your memory, you may not take notes about the picture.
fields.interaction_instructions:
Using the knowledge you have gained from viewing Picture 1 in your teams, answer the following questions. Please write answers next to the approprate number.. You will have 3 minutes to complete this task.

  1. What color is the flag in the picture?
  2. Is a person playing a violin in the picture?
  3. How many tables are being used to eat on in the picture?

For future memory tasks, you may use the chat to discuss strategies with your teammates in order to remember as much as possible.
